<taxonomicName authorityName="Milne-Edwards" authorityYear="1867" box="[889,1067,1557,1586]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Cricetulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="longicaudatus">longicaudatus</taxonomicName>
group. Three subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
